Class PrimProcedure

        +--com.ibm.jikes.skij.PrimProcedure
public abstract class PrimProcedure
extends Procedure

This abstract class represents primitve procedures (those implemented in Java). The individual primitives are defined as inner classes based on this. Most but not all are defined in this file. Each inner class defines its own apply method that contains the definition.
